title: Rinne no Lagrange (Lagrange: The Flower of Rin-ne)
synopsis: Madoka Kyouno is an energetic girl who is full of passion. As the proud, and only, member of the Kamogawa Girls' High School Jersey Club, she goes around helping people in need.
